metadata.name: Fearless
metadata.description:
She walked down into the depths of hell to face her demon. She knew his name and knew his ways and knew that this would cost her greatly. She also knew that she was willing to pay that cost to be free of this demon. 
She stood before his monstrous being and his fiery breath wore her down to almost nothing. She felt something within her change when she stood her ground. She was something else. Ready to face the next demon.
